snippet.title: Sonic Robo Blast (SRB1) | SAGE 2020 Demo
snippet.description:
It's here! The ambitious update to the first full Sonic fan game ever developed has gotten a demo release at this year's SAGE. SRB1, having been finished in 1998, was quickly overshadowed by its still-in-active-development sequel. This upcoming official update is set to finally give it the overhaul it deserves.

You can download this demo here: https://www.sonicfangameshq.com/forums/showcase/sonic-robo-blast-knothole-coast-demo.678/
